original: Kling, Calla, tandläkare, Göteborg, f. 18/7/09 i Gbg av kont :chefen John Agvald o. Agda Andersson. G. 37 m. tandl. Östen Kling. Barn: Kristina f. 41, Marianne 42, Eva Helena 44. — Stud:ex. v. Gbgs h. samsk. 29, tysk tandl. 33, sv. dito 34. Prakt, i Sten-ungsund o. Gbg sed. 34.
translated: Kling, Calla, dentist, Gothenburg, b. 18/7/09 in Gothenburg, daughter of the accountant John Agvald and Agda Andersson. Married in 1937 to dentist Östen Kling. Children: Kristina b. 1941, Marianne b. 1942, Eva Helena b. 1944. — Attended the student exam at Gothenburg high school in 1929, studied German dentistry in 1933, Swedish dentistry in 1934. Practiced in Stenungsund and Gothenburg since 1934.
